title: Miley Cyrus Went on an Instagram Spree at Her Family Farm - Miley Cyrus Family Reunion
text:
Miley Cyrus took a break from bouncing between Hollywood and Australia to head back to Nashville for a family reunion on a farm, ET Online reports. (Honestly, it makes sense that Miley wants to hang out with adorable farm animals since she's vegan AF .)
